Celkon is a mobile phone manufacturing company in India based in Hyderabad. It is involved in the development of mobile phones, Tablet PCs, and wireless technologies. Currently the Managing Director of Celkon Mobiles is Y.Guru
Celkon is India's sixth-largest mobile handsets company. Initially its mobiles and tablet PCs was assembled in Taiwan and China. Later the company established its own manufacturing facility in the Telangana state of India.
